metadata.description: This is a commemorative ticket that welcomes newcomers into the Cryptovoxels space and also invites them to visit our 'Last Confirmation' art gallery, in world.  This series is a collaborative blockchain fine art collection between Norman Harman and myself Robness Cyberpop.  Currently this month we have 3 works that are being displayed in 3 different parts of the globe(February 2020).  One being the NFT.NYC event in New York, one at the 'Cryptoque' art show in Madrid, Spain and one at the 'Digital Renaissance' show in London, England which is a show thrown by Sascha Bailey.  We hope you enjoy the works and here is the coordinates to the gallery, thank you!.... https://www.cryptovoxels.com/play?coords=W@136E,376S
metadata.name: Last Confirmation VR Art Gallery Token Invitation
